{
  "text": "Incorporation of biologically active molecules, particularly growth factors with platelets as the source has yielded promising results. This evinced clinical interest in platelet derived products and lead to the evolution of platelet concentrates; first generation platelet concentrates such as platelet \u2212 rich plasma (PRP) and second generation such as platelet-rich fibrin (PRF) [CITATION_1] .",
